      "content": "that makes sense, but i'm trying to get more specific. i've heard a lot of folks saying that these hikes are basically a death sentence for small shops in rural areas because we just can't compete with the big corporations. do you think that's a fair assessment of the actual economic reality, or is that just political talk?",
